Introduction

Choi Yoonjung is a South Korean trainee.

She is a former pre-debut member of the trainee girl group CSR (formerly known as 05Class).

Yoonjung is also known for being a contestant on the survival show My Teenage Girl, where she ranked 14th and was eliminated.
